<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Liz Charvet</ENAMEX> with <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Teddy Bear Corner</ENAMEX> said the children and their families sold 712 pizza kits to raise funds for the project. She said this is the most money the children have ever helped raise for a cause.
